</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">About</div></div><div class="u-text-size-large">Team Surf Haven</div></div><div class="about-body"><p>None of us set out to build this. Milo came to clear his head, Tess was dodging burnout, Rafa was outrunning a rough year. Jade and Ren came for a month and never booked the flight home. We met by accident — in the lineup, at a beach bar, one of us at a bonfire — started sharing rides and helping with each other's odd jobs, and eventually admitted we made a decent team with the same daft idea: what if we ran a surf camp? That was a few seasons ago. <br><br><strong>A good number of camps later, all we're really trying to do is hand you the same feeling that made every one of us stay.</strong></p></div></div><div class="about-image"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/team-portrait-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/team-portrait-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/team-portrait.avif 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" src="/assets/img/team-portrait.avif" width="900" height="1010" alt="A cheerful group portrait of five young people posing playfully with thumbs-up gestures against a tropical background of palm trees."></div><div data-w-id="51d37ca7-1631-62e1-4595-ff643a85614b" class="close-button"><div class="x-close-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-x-icon lucide-x"><path d="M18 6 6 18"></path><path d="m6 6 12 12"></path></svg></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-overview" class="section-overview"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical is-double-top"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid layout-grid"><div id="w-node-_4ef50234-6607-ca98-5d4f-7d69c383a6b3-f2b4ae30" class="w-layout-grid overview-header"><div class="title-wrap"