</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">overview</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="Trade your desk for a week of paradise — Bali"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">Trade your desk </div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line2-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line2" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">for a week of </div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line3-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line3" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">paradise — <span class="heading-accent"></span><span class="heading-accent">Bali</span></div></div></h2></div><div class="tag-list"><div class="tag-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Perfect Swells</div></div><div class="tag-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Warm Waters</div></div><div class="tag-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" vie