</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">Levels</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="There's a wave for your&nbsp;level"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">There's a </div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line2-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line2" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">wave for your <span class="heading-accent"></span><span class="heading-accent">level</span></div></div></h2></div><a id="w-node-_2704896c-3de3-55f5-e1d5-f6b918351b71-f2b4ae30" data-w-id="2704896c-3de3-55f5-e1d5-f6b918351b71" href="#section-program" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>See Full Program</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div><div class="w-layout-grid layout-cards"><div id="w-node-_94ea0941-3c75-c816-7244-83836e27ee25-f2b4ae30" class="levels-card"><div class="u-flex-row"><div class="image-circle-wrap"><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" alt="" src="/assets/img/surfboard-on-grass.webp"></div><div class="badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><div>first-time</div></div></div><div class="levels-card-content"><div class="levels-card-header"><h3>Total Newbie</h3><div class="chevron-button is-hidden-desktop"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>Zero experience? Perfect. We begin on the sand — balance, timing, and how to stay calm in the water — before you ever paddle out. Most people are riding whitewater by the end of day one.</p></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_94ea0941-3c75-c816-7244-83836e27ee37-f2b4ae30" class="levels-card"><div class="u-flex-row"><div class="image-circle-wrap"><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" alt="" src="/assets/img/surfboard-feet-action.webp"></div><div class="badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><div>beginner</div></div></div><div class="levels-card-content"><div class="levels-card-header"><h3>Still Learning</h3><div class="chevron-button is-hidden-desktop"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>You can stand up and ride the foam. Now we tidy up the basics and get you turning down the line on unbroken waves, with plenty of coaching along the way.</p></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_94ea0941-3c75-c816-7244-83836e27ee49-f2b4ae30" class="levels-card"><div class="u-flex-row"><div class="image-circle-wrap"><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" alt="" src="/assets/img/man-surfing-wave.webp"></div><div class="badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><div>intermediate</div></div></div><div class="levels-card-content"><div class="levels-card-header"><h3>Pretty Confident</h3><div class="chevron-button is-hidden-desktop"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>You're comfortable out the back and hungry to get sharper. We'll take you to punchier peaks and fine-tune the details that separate riding from surfing.</p></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_94ea0941-3c75-c816-7244-83836e27ee5b-f2b4ae30" class="levels-card"><div class="u-flex-row"><div class="image-circle-wrap"><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" alt="" src="/assets/img/shaka-hand.webp"></div><div class="badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><div>advanced</div></div></div><div class="levels-card-content"><div class="levels-card-header"><h3>Already a Pro</h3><div class="chevron-button is-hidden-desktop"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>You don't need lessons — you need good waves and good company. Join the dawn patrol, trade pointers with the crew, and just surf.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-stay" class="section-stay"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical"><div id="w-node-