</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">experience</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="Sun, salt, and&nbsp;everything&nbsp;in between"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">Sun, salt, and </div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line2-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line2" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">everything <span class="heading-accent">in </span></div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line3-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line3" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start"><span class="heading-accent">between</span></div></div></h2></div><p>The waves are the reason you came. The rest is why you'll come back.</p></div><a aria-label="Join the camp – experience" data-w-id="286fe33e-7a7f-47fd-3edd-63a611260901" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div id="w-node-_309f40c5-e3b5-1b6c-5dea-79914643a661-f2b4ae30" class="experience-column-right"><div class="w-layout-grid experience-cards"><div id="w-node-_309f40c5-e3b5-1b6c-5dea-79914643a663-f2b4ae30" class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for body</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Yoga and Meditation</h3><p>Loosen up sore shoulders with an evening flow, and ease into the day with an unhurried morning sit before the first session.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/waterfall.avif" class="emoji"></div></div><div id="w-node-_309f40c5-e3b5-1b6c-5dea-79914643a66f-f2b4ae30" class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for soul</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Temples and Ceremonies</h3><p>Slow down for a temple morning and the odd fireside circle, where the conversation tends to drift somewhere honest.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/villa-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/villa-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/villa.avif 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/villa.avif" class="emoji"></div></div><div class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for mind</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Culture and Growth </h3><p>Wander the markets with someone who knows them, then linger over dinners that go long past the last plate.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/surfing.avif" class="emoji"></div></div><div class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for fun</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Adventures Together</h3><p>Chase quiet coves on two wheels, graze your way through a night market, and stay up telling stories you'll retell for years.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/surfers.avif" class="emoji"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-cta-1" class="section-cta"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical is-half-mobile"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard is-radius-card-outer w-container"><div class="layout-centered is-cta"><div class="cta-content u-text-color-white"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 12 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
