</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">program</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="What we’ve planned&nbsp;for you:"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">What we’ve <span class="heading-accent"></span><span class="heading-accent">planned</span> for you:</div></div></h2></div><a id="w-node-_06f4356d-4b9c-5657-2da9-36b6ad783e8c-f2b4ae30" data-w-id="06f4356d-4b9c-5657-2da9-36b6ad783e8c" href="/assets/Surf Camp Program.pdf" class="tertiary-button w-inline-block"><div class="download-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-download-icon lucide-download"><path d="M12 15V3"></path><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><path d="m7 10 5 5 5-5"></path></svg></div><div class="button-text-wrap"><div class="button-text">Full Program</div></div></a></div><div class="program-body"><div class="day-list"><div class="day-accordion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 1</div><h3>Landing Day &amp; First Faces</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="follow-cursor-wrap" style="display: flex"><div class="follow-cursor"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/friends-cocktails-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/friends-cocktails-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/friends-cocktails.avif 928w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="928" height="1232" alt="A group of smiling friends enjoying colorful summer cocktails and cold drinks in an outdoor tropical garden setting." src="/assets/img/friends-cocktails.avif"></div></div><div class="line-fill-wrap"><div class="line-fill-color"></div><div class="line-base u-absolute-full"></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="day-tabs-wrap"><div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="day-tabs-parent w-tabs"><div id="w-node-_3589fdf6-24ea-7cde-8070-541cac23e1dc-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-menu w-tab-menu" role="tablist"><a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" id="w-tabs-0-data-w-tab-0" href="#w-tabs-0-data-w-pane-0" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-0-data-w-pane-0" aria-selected="true"><div>Description</div></a><a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" tabindex="-1" id="w-tabs-0-data-w-tab-1" href="#w-tabs-0-data-w-pane-1" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-0-data-w-pane-1" aria-selected="false"><div>Timetable</div></a></div><div id="w-node-_3589fdf6-24ea-7cde-8070-541cac23e1e3-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-content w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" id="w-tabs-0-data-w-pane-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-0-data-w-tab-0"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-pane-text"><p>Landing day. This one's about arriving properly — we'll collect you from the airport whenever you land, settle you into your room, and let island time do its thing. Nothing on the schedule but introductions, something cold by the pool, and an easy dinner together. By the end of the night the group won't feel new anymore.</p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 1" data-w-id="54379bc5-00b7-85bf-f881-30822db499d6" href="#" class=