></div></div><div>Easy villa hangout, getting to know the crew</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>23:00+</div></div><div>Crash early or keep talking</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 2</div><h3>First Waves &amp; Finding Your Feet</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="follow-cursor-wrap" style="display: flex"><div class="follow-cursor"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/surfers-palm-garden-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/surfers-palm-garden-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/surfers-palm-garden.avif 928w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="928" height="1232" alt="Two women in swimwear carrying surfboards while walking across a lush green lawn through a grove of palm trees toward the beach." src="/assets/img/surfers-palm-garden.avif"></div></div><div class="line-fill-wrap"><div class="line-fill-color"></div><div class="line-base u-absolute-full"></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="day-tabs-wrap"><div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="day-tabs-parent w-tabs"><div id="w-node-_3589fdf6-24ea-7cde-8070-541cac23e267-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-menu w-tab-menu" role="tablist"><a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" id="w-tabs-1-data-w-tab-0" href="#w-tabs-1-data-w-pane-0" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-1-data-w-pane-0" aria-selected="true"><div>Description</div></a><a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" tabindex="-1" id="w-tabs-1-data-w-tab-1" href="#w-tabs-1-data-w-pane-1" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-1-data-w-pane-1" aria-selected="false"><div>Timetable</div></a></div><div id="w-node-_3589fdf6-24ea-7cde-8070-541cac23e26e-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-content w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" id="w-tabs-1-data-w-pane-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-1-data-w-tab-0"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-pane-text"><p>First real day in the water. We start easy at a gentle break while the coaches read everyone's level and sort the groups. In the afternoon we find our feet with a scooter loop around town, and we cap the night at a local warung for the proper stuff.<br></p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 2" data-w-id="409a8475-a7ca-baca-c664-cab6ddbee788" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="day-pane-image"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/surfers-palm-garden-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/surfers-palm-garden-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/surfers-palm-garden.avif 928w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="928" height="1232" alt="Two women in swimwear carrying surfboards while walking across a lush green lawn through a grove of palm trees toward the beach." src="/assets/img/surfers-palm-garden.avif"></div></div></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane" id="w-tabs-1-data-w-pane-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-1-data-w-tab-1"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-timetable"><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>07:00-07:30</div></div><div>Morning wake-up</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>07:30-08:30 </div></div><div>Villa breakfast</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:30-09:00 </div></div><div>Ride out to the break</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>09:00-09:45</div></div><div>On-sand session — surf basics and safety</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>09:45-11:30 </div></div><div>First proper paddle-out</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>11:30-12:00 </div></div><div>Head back to the villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>12:00-13:00 </div></div><div>Rinse off and change</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>13:00-14:00</div></div><div>Lunch by the beach</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>14:00-14:30 </div></div><div>Two-wheel safety run-through</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>14:30-17:30 </div></div><div>Scooter loop around town</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>17:30-18:30 </div></div><div>Downtime at the villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>18:30-19:30 </div></div><div>Golden-hour yoga on the deck</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>19:30-20:00 </div></div><div>Freshen up</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>20:00-21:30 </div></div><div>Dinner at a neighbourhood warung</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>21:30-23:00</div></div><div>Evening stroll or villa chill</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>23:00-06:30</div></div><div>Sleep</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 3</div><h3>Sharper Turns &amp; Beach Club</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="follow-cursor-wrap" style="display: flex"><div class="follow-cursor"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/dj-outdoor-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/dj-outdoor-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/dj-outdoor.avif 928w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="928" height="1233" alt="DJ wearing headphones playing music on a mixer at a tropical outdoor party with people dancing among palm trees." src="/assets/img/dj-outdoor.avif"></div></div><div class="line-fill-wrap"><div class="line-fill-color"></div><div class="line-base u-absolute-full"></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="day-tabs-wrap"><div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="day-tabs-parent w-tabs"><div id="w-node-_3589fdf6-24ea-7cde-8070-541cac23e2f2-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-menu w-tab-menu" role="tablist"><a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" id="w-tabs-2-data-w-tab-0" href="#w-tabs-2-data-w-pane-0" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-2-data-w-pane-0" aria-selected="true"><div>Description</div></a><a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" tabindex="-1" id="w-tabs-2-data-w-tab-1" href="#w-tabs-2-data-w-pane-1" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-2-data-w-pane-1" aria-selected="false"><div>Timetable</div></a></div><div id="w-node-_3589fdf6-24ea-7cde-8070-541cac23e2f9-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-content w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" id="w-tabs-2-data-w-pane-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-2-data-w-tab-0"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-pane-text"><p>A morning built around the details — cleaner pop-ups, better positioning, reading the sets. You'll notice the difference from yesterday. The afternoon eases off at a beach club for a long lunch and a swim. Sun, music, salt water, and a group that's stopped feeling like strangers.</p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 3" data-w-id="fd89a7bd-b829-f2a7-f267-039c6d981ce5" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="day-pane-image"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/dj-outdoor-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/dj-outdoor-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/dj-outdoor.avif 928w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="928" height="1233" alt="DJ wearing headphones playing music on a mixer at a tropical outdoor party with people dancing among palm trees." src="/assets/img/dj-outdoor.avif"></div></div></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane" id="w-tabs-2-data-w-pane-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-2-data-w-tab-1"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-timetable"><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>06:30-07:00</div></div><div>Morning start</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>07:00-08:00 </div></div><div>Morning meal</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:00-08:30 </div></div><div>Ride out to the break</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:30-11:30 </div></div><div>Surf — dialling in technique</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>11:30-12:00 </div></div><div>Off to the beach club</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>12:00-17:00 </div></div><div>Beach club afternoon — lunch, pool, music, sun</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>17:00-17:30</div></div><div>Head back to the villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>17:30-19:00 </div></div><div>Villa downtime</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>19:00-19:30</div></div><div>Fire up the grill together</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>19:30-21:00 </div></div><div>Grill night at the villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>21:00-22:30 </div></div><div>Movie night in</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>22:30-00:00 </div></div><div>Bonfire on the sand</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>00:00-08:00</div></div><div>Sleep</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 4<br></div><h3>Temple Morning &amp; Island Culture</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fil