orning at one of the island's clifftop temples, then eat somewhere with a view. The afternoon is for a local market — souvenirs, snacks you've never tried, and a bit of everyday culture. Dinner tonight is the slow, get-to-know-everyone kind.<br></p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 4" data-w-id="ddde2833-7c73-9ee5-e018-cfa7fe44ab6c" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="day-pane-image"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/jungle-temple-mist-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/jungle-temple-mist-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/jungle-temple-mist.avif 928w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="928" height="1232" alt="A traditional multi-tiered Balinese temple nestled among dense, misty green jungle foliage under a hazy sky." src="/assets/img/jungle-temple-mist.avif"></div></div></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane" id="w-tabs-3-data-w-pane-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-3-data-w-tab-1"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-timetable"><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:00-08:30</div></div><div>Morning start</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:30-09:30 </div></div><div>Morning meal</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>09:30-10:00 </div></div><div>Set off for the temple</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>10:00-12:30 </div></div><div>Clifftop temple visit</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div clas