day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>21:30-23:00 </div></div><div>Beach bonfire, sharing the week's highlights</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>23:00-01:00 </div></div><div>Last night of music and memories</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>01:00-07:00</div></div><div>Sleep</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-instructors" class="section-instructors"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid layout-grid"><div id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cd9b-f2b4ae30" class="slider-wrap"><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="slider is-instructors w-slider" data-autoplay="false" data-easing="ease" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="500" data-infinite="true" role="region" aria-label="carousel"><div class="w-slider-mask" id="w-slider-mask-1"><div class="slide is-instructors w-slide" aria-label="1 of 2" role="group" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/5010 1-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/5010 1-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/5010 1-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/img/5010 1.webp 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" src="/assets/img/5010 1.webp" width="940" height="854" alt="A smiling professional surf instructor in a black wetsuit holding a white surfboard against a lush tropical jungle background."></div><div class="slide-content"><div class="slide-popup"><div class="slide-popup-content"><div class="slide-popup-heading">Ketut Rai</div><div>I grew up a few streets from this beach and have been paddling out since before I can properly remember. Coaching isn't a job to me so much as an excuse to show people around the place I love. My favourite part is the first real wave — the second it clicks and the ocean does the work for you. <br><br>First time on your feet or chasing a cleaner turn, I'll be right beside you in the lineup — keeping it safe, keeping it fun, and making sure you actually leave better than you arrived. That's the whole aim.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Coach: Ketut Rai</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost"><div class="plus-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>ENG / IND</div></div></div></div></div><div data-w-id="43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cdb5" class="slide is-instructors w-slide" aria-label="2 of 2" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/surf-coach-02-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/surf-coach-02-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/surf-coach-02-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/img/surf-coach-02.webp 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" src="/assets/img/surf-coach-02.webp" width="1360" height="1237" alt="A portrait of a friendly man in a wetsuit posing with his surfboard in front of vibrant green palm leaves." aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Cody Nolan</div><div aria-hidden="true">I came up surfing points back home in Australia, booked a two-week trip over here years ago, and quietly forgot to leave. The waves are worth the flight, but it was the pace of life and the people that actually kept me. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">I got into coaching after watching one too many visitors get handed nonsense on the sand. I'd rather teach it right — how to stay safe, how to read the day, how to actually move on a board. Beginner or brushing up on turns, I'll break it down piece by piece and keep it fun the whole way through.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Coach: Cody Nolan </div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">ENG / IND / ESP</div></div></div></div></div><div aria-live="off" aria-atomic="true" class="w-slider-aria-label" data-wf-ignore=""></div></div><div class="left-arrow is-frost-on-image u-absolute-bottom-right w-slider-arrow-left" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-1" aria-label="previous slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="right-arrow is-frost-on-image u-absolute-bottom-right w-slider-arrow-right" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-1" aria-label="next slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="slide-nav is-hidden w-slider-nav"><div class="w-slider-dot w-active" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 1 of 2" aria-pressed="true" role="button" tabindex="0" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div><div class="w-slider-dot" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 2 of 2" aria-pressed="false" role="button" tabindex="-1" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cdd1-f2b4ae30" class="heading-wrap is-small"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 12 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
