</svg></div><blockquote>Honestly the best thing I did all year. I turned up fried from work and left feeling like a person again. The coaching is legit, nobody takes themselves too seriously, and I somehow collected friends from four continents. Went from wobbling to actually riding — and I've already rebooked.</blockquote></div><div class="testimonial-author u-text-size-small"><div><strong>Marco Ferretti</strong></div><div class="u-text-color-muted">Surf Haven, August 2025</div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-testimonials w-slide" aria-label="2 of 3" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="u-flex-row" aria-hidden="true"><div class="image-circle-wrap" aria-hidden="true"><img loading="lazy" width="300" height="300" alt="A smiling woman with freckles and dark hair styled in two buns, wearing a yellow tank top and a heart necklace against a blurred green background." src="/assets/img/check.webp" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="badge" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">camp '25</div></div></div><div class="testimonial-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="quote-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 31 27" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
