</svg></div><blockquote aria-hidden="true">I nearly bailed because I was going solo, and within an evening that worry was gone. Surf in the mornings, explore in the afternoons, and the sort of late conversations you normally only have with people you've known for years. Already scheming a way back.</blockquote></div><div class="testimonial-author u-text-size-small" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true"><strong aria-hidden="true">Yuki Tanaka</strong></div><div class="u-text-color-muted" aria-hidden="true">Surf Haven, March 2025</div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-testimonials w-slide" aria-label="3 of 3" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="u-flex-row" aria-hidden="true"><div class="image-circle-wrap" aria-hidden="true"><img loading="lazy" width="300" height="300" alt="A joyful woman with long, curly blonde hair laughing heartily, set against a soft-focus natural green background." src="/assets/img/4487 1.webp" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="badge" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">camp '24</div></div></div><div class="testimonial-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="quote-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 31 27" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
