</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">TEAM</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="Meet the team"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">Meet the team</div></div></h2></div><p>The people who actually run your week</p></div><div id="w-node-_22fe9cd3-bc58-b1f9-ea5d-f6753de580bf-f2b4ae30" class="team-body"><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="slider is-team w-slider" data-autoplay="false" data-easing="ease-in-out" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="500" data-infinite="true" role="region" aria-label="carousel"><div class="team-slider-mask w-slider-mask" id="w-slider-mask-3"><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="1 of 5" role="group" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/Frame 1618873057-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/Frame 1618873057-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/Frame 1618873057.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="900" height="1232" alt="A man wearing an orange propeller hat and sunglasses, gesturing with his hands in front of large tropical palm leaves." src="/assets/img/Frame 1618873057.webp"></div><div class="slide-content"><div class="slide-popup"><div class="slide-popup-content"><div class="slide-popup-heading">Milo Hart</div><div>I want your week to be spent on real things — chasing waves, doing something that scares you a little, and being around people who get it. I turned up here years ago with no plan, and surfing this coast quietly rearranged how I look at most things. Nothing dramatic. Just clearer. <br><br>And the rest of the crew — we all pull in the same direction to make sure no day gets wasted.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Milo</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost"><div class="plus-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Founder</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="2 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="900" height="1232" alt="A smiling woman with long dark hair and facial piercings, holding her hand out toward the camera in a tropical setting." src="/assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR.webp" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Tess Okafor</div><div aria-hidden="true">I've somehow landed the job I'd have made up as a kid — camera in hand, on the beach all day, meeting people from everywhere and telling their stories in photos and clips. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">The shot I'm always chasing is the first stand-up — the look on someone's face is impossible to fake. I also run our socials and keep everyone connected after camp, so tag us and don't be shy about it.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Tess</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">SMM guru</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="3 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="900" height="1233" alt="A man with dark hair laughing heartily with his head tilted back, set against a blurred green foliage background." src="/assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u.webp" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Rafa Mendes</div><div aria-hidden="true">I'm usually the first person you'll hear from when you're weighing this up, and I'll shoot straight with you — no pitch, just an honest read on which option actually fits. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">Once you land, my whole job is making sure the group clicks and nobody feels on the outside. A nudge before you paddle out or a cold one after sunset — either way I've got you. Your week genuinely matters to me.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Rafa</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Sales Manager</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="4 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="900" height="1233" alt="A man with short curly hair smiling warmly with his arms crossed, wearing a black t-shirt in front of palm trees." src="/assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1.webp" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Ren Alvarez</div><div aria-hidden="true">I know 'logistics' sounds dull, but it's quietly the thing that makes or breaks a week. I sweat the details — your room being ready, the right break for the day's conditions, breakfast on time, drivers where they should be. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">A few years on the island means I know the quiet spots the guidebooks miss. Really, I carry the planning stress so you can turn up and just enjoy it.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Tyler</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Coordinator</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="5 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 50vw, 640px" width="900" height="1200" alt="A woman with short blonde hair winking and making an &quot;OK&quot; hand gesture while smiling in a lush green outdoor environment." src="/assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1.webp" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Jade Okoye</div><div aria-hidden="true">I run the good stuff — bonfires on the sand, temple and waterfall runs, morning yoga, game nights, whatever makes the week stick. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">A good week is about balance — so while you're grinding in the water, I make sure there's room to explore, switch off, and actually get to know the group. My job is to keep the energy up on the board and off it.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Jade</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Event Manager</div></div></div></div></div><div aria-live="off" aria-atomic="true" class="w-slider-aria-label" data-wf-ignore=""></div></div><div class="left-arrow u-absolute-top-right is-offset w-slider-arrow-left" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-3" aria-label="previous slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="right-arrow u-absolute-top-right is-offset w-slider-arrow-right" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-3" aria-label="next slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="slide-nav is-hidden w-slider-nav"><div class="w-slider-dot w-active" data-wf-ignore="" aria-